org.afplib.afplib

Interface UniversalDateAndTimeStamp

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UniversalDateAndTimeStampImpl

    public interface UniversalDateAndTimeStamp
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Universal Date And Time Stamp'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Reserved
    • Year AD
    • Month
    • Day
    • Hour
    • Minute
    • Second
    • Time Zone
    • UTC Diff H
    • UTC Diff M

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getUniversalDateAndTimeStamp()
